s="function">\n        <h1>void category(string category_id,string start)<a href="#top" name="category" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            category_id：分类编号<br />\n            start：当前页面号，默认第一页(可选)<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">显示分类列表文章，支持后台管理中，自定义模板，子定义模板格式article_category_{0}，参数为模板定义名称</div>\n        <h3>Return</h3>\n        <div class="content">\n            category：分类对象<br />\n            articles：文章数组<br />\n            index：当前页面索引号<br />\n            size：分页大小<br />\n            total：总记录数<br />\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>void page(string page_id)<a href="#top" name="page" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            page_id：页面编号<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">显示单页面内容</div>\n        <h3>Return</h3>\n        <div class="content">\n            content：内容对象<br />\n            content.Image_id：当前页面的图片对象，如果页面没有图片，则继承上一级页面图片<br />\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>void tag(string tag_id, string start)<a href="#top" name="tag" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            tag_id：标签编号<br />\n            start：当前页面号，默认第一页(可选)<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">显示标签下的文章列表，支持后台管理中，自定义模板</div>\n        <h3>Return</h3>\n        <div class="content">\n            category：标签所属的分类对象<br />\n            articles：文章数组<br />\n            index：当前页面索引号<br />\n            size：分页大小<br />\n            total：总记录数<br />\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>void detail(string article_id)<a href="#top" name="detail" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            article_id：文章编号<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">显示文章详细内容</div>\n        <h3>Return</h3>\n        <div class="content">\n            article：文章对象<br />\n            content：文章内容<br />\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>set_hot(string article_id)<a href="#top" name="set_hot" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            article_id：文章编号<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">通过ajax现实推荐文章，推荐成功返回：success</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>void click(string code_id)<a href="#top" name="click" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            code_id：广告位编号<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">广告链接跳转，如果没有设置目标地址，则跳到首页。第一次点击后会留下名为：jabinfo_ads的cookie，保存30天，值是code_id</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>void message()<a href="#top" name="message" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">显示留言页面,addmessage页面是接受留言的目标地址，每个用户，每次最多留言10个</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>void login()<a href="#top" name="login" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">用户登录页面</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>void register()<a href="#top" name="register" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">用户注册页面</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>MessageVO[] message(string object_id , int length)<a href="#top" name="api_message" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            object_id：评论对象<br />\n            length：获取的评论数<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">只获取审核通过的评论</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>MessageVO[] hot_msg(string object_id,int length)<a href="#top" name="hot_msg" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            object_id：评论对象<br />\n            length：获取的评论数<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">获取star标签等于5的评论</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>MessageVO[] rank(int length)<a href="#top" name="rank" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            length：获取的评论数<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">获取置首的评论</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>ArticleVO[] category(string category_id,int length)<a href="#top" name="api_category" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            category_id：分类编号<br />\n            length：获取文章数<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">获取该分类下的文章</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>ArticleVO[] tag(string tag_id ,int length)<a href="#top" name="api_tag" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            tag_id：标签编号<br />\n            length：获取文章数<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">获取标签下文章</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>ArticleVO[] complex(string category_id,string tag_id,int length)<a href="#top" name="complex" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            category_id：分类编号<br />\n            tag_id：标签编号<br />\n            length：获取文章数<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">获取分类标签下的文章</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>ArticleVO[] week(int length)<a href="#top" name="week" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            length：获取的文章数<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">每周热门文章</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>ArticleVO[] weekByCategory(string relate_id,int length)<a href="#top" name="weekByCategory" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            relate_id：分类或标签编号<br />\n            length：获取的文章数<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">获取分类或标签下的每周热点</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="function">\n        <h1>PageVO[] page(string jtype)<a href="#top" name="api_page" class="small">back</a></h1>\n        <div class="content">\n            jtype：组编号<br />\n        </div>\n        <h3>Note</h3>\n        <div class="content">获取一组页面</div>\n    </div>\n    <br />\n</div>\n?template("help_foot")?', '1002032132328300875', 1339501310, 1339501310, '1002032132328300875', 8, '');
