 onclick="pingstar(1)"></span>\n						<span class="talkx1" id="star2" onclick="pingstar(2)"></span>\n						<span class="talkx1" id="star3" onclick="pingstar(3)"></span>\n						<span class="talkx1" id="star4" onclick="pingstar(4)"></span>\n						<span class="talkx1" id="star5" onclick="pingstar(5)"></span>\n						<span class="talktest">点击星星就可以评分了</span>\n					</dd>\n				</dl>\n				<dl><dt>评论标题：</dt>\n					<dd><input name="title" id="input1212" class="talkinp1" type="text" maxlength="20" /></dd>\n					<dd>&nbsp;&nbsp;<em>*</em></dd>\n				</dl>\n				<dl><dt>评论内容：</dt>\n					<dd><textarea class="talkinp2" maxlength="300" name="content" id="content_msg" > </textarea></dd>\n					<dd class="col999">&nbsp;&nbsp;最多可输入300字</dd>\n			    </dl>\n				<dl><dt></dt>\n					<dd><input type="button" class="talkinp" value="" onclick="return addmsgfun();" ></dd>\n				</dl>\n			</form>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n<input id="isgoumai11" type="hidden" value="?isgoumai?"/>\n\n<div id="logtan1" style="display:none;" class="logtancss">\n<div class="logtan" style="height:232px;">\n	<h3><span style="width:200px; font-weight: normal;">暂时不能对商品进行评价</span><a href="javascript:void(0)" title="关闭" onclick="colselogtan()"></a></h3>\n    <div class="logtaninfo">\n    	<dl style="border-bottom:1px dashed #ddd; font-size:13px; font-weight:bold; margin:0px; height:38px; margin-bottom:15px; line-height:38px;">\n        	抱歉，您暂时不能对商品进程评价，可能有以下原因：\n        </dl>\n    	<dl style="margin-bottom:0px;">\n        	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、您可能没有在好开门购买过该商品。\n        </dl> \n    	<dl style="margin-bottom:0px;">\n        	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、您购买了该商品，但没有确认收货，或订单还未完成。\n        </dl>\n    	<dl style="margin-bottom:0px;">\n        	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、您已经评价过该商品\n        </dl>\n        <dl style="margin-bottom:0px;">\n        	<dt>&nbsp;</dt>\n        	<dd><input name="" class="user_chonginp1" style="height:29px; line-height:29px; text-align:center; margin-left:66px; _margin-left:45px;" value="确定" type="button" onclick="colselogtan()" /></dd>\n        </dl>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--//商品发表评价弹出框结束-->\n\n\n\n<script type="text/javascript">\n /*评论 好| 中| 差  的切换*/\n    function showmsgg(_id){\n		up(''?site("product/home/detailmsg")?/?product_id?/''+_id,''pro_eva'');\n    }\n \n/*发表评论*/\nvar absfalsg1=true;\nvar msgcount1=1;\nvar isgoumai1=true;\nif($(''#isgoumai11'').val()=="0")\n{\nisgoumai1=false;\n}\nvar goumai_str1="";\nfunction addmsgfun(){\n	if($(''#stars'').val()==0){alert(''请先评论商品满意度'');return false;}\n	if(!isgoumai1){alert(goumai_str1);return false;}\n	if(msgcount>10){goumai_str1="请不要频繁留言";alert(goumai_str1);isgoumai1=false;return false;}\n	if($(''#input1212'').val()==''''){alert(''评论标题不能为空'');return false;}\n    if(!absfalsg1){return false;}\n    absfalsg1=false;\n    setTimeout(function(){absfalsg1=true;},2500);\n	msgcount1++;\n    $.ajax({\n        url: $(''#messagestar'').attr(''action''),\n        type: ''POST'',\n        data: $(''#messagestar'').serialize(),\n        async: false,\n		error:function(datas){alert(''发表评论出错，请重试'');return false; },\n        success:function(msg){\n			absfalsg1=true;\n			if(msg!=''''){\n				switch(msg)\n				{\n case ''-4'':is_qingxinglogin=true;login(addmsgfun);break;\n					case ''-1'': $(''#talk'').hide();$(''#logtan1'').show();isgoumai1=false;break;\n					case ''-2'':alert("评论失败，请刷新页面重试");break;\n					case ''-3'': $(''#talk'').hide();$(''#logtan1'').show();break;\n                    case ''-5'':goumai_str1="企业用户不能发表评论";alert(goumai_str1);isgoumai1=false;break;\n case ''-6'':$(''#talk'').hide();$(''#logtan1'').show();break;\n					case ''1'':alert("评论成功");break;\n					default:alert(msg);break;\n				}\n				closemessage();\n				return true;	\n			}\n		}\n    });\n	return true;\n}\n \n /*开启 评论窗口*/\nfunction showmessage(){\n	login(showmessage_fun);	\n}\nfunction showmessage_fun()\n{\n$.get("?site(''deal/member/compareNick'')?",null,callbacknick);	\n}\n function callbacknick(data)\n{\nif(data==username)\n{\nvar message="为了您帐号的安全，请先修改昵称后再评论！";\nwindow.location.href=''?site(''deal/member/updateNick'')?/product/?product_id?/''+message;\nreturn false;\n}\nelse\n{\nif(!isgoumai1){$(''#logtan1'').show();return false;}\n	if(msgcount1>2){alert(''请不要频繁评论'');return false;}\n    if(!absfalsg1){alert(''正在发表评论，请稍候'');return false;}\n	$(''#talk'').show();\n	return true;\n}\n}\n /*点击评论星级*/\nfunction pingstar(st){\n	if($(''#star''+st).hasClass(''talkx1'')){\n        for(var i=1;i<=st;i++){\n			$(''#star''+i).removeClass("talkx1").addClass("talkx2");\n        } \n    }\n	else{\n        for(var i=5;i>st;i--){\n			$(''#star''+i).removeClass("talkx2").addClass("talkx1");\n        } \n    }   \n    $("#stars").val(st);  \n}\n \n /*关闭 评论窗口*/\nfunction closemessage(){\n$(''#stars'').val(''0'');\n    $(''#talk'').hide();\n	for(var i=1;i<=5;i++){\n		$("#star"+i).removeClass("talkx2").addClass("talkx1");\n	} \n	$(''#input1212'').val('''');\n	$(''#content_msg'').val('''');\n}\n function colselogtan()\n{\n$(''#stars'').val(''0'');\n$(''#logtan1'').hide();\nfor(var i=1;i<=5;i++){\n$("#star"+i).removeClass("talkx2").addClass("talkx1");\n	} \n	$(''#input1212'').val('''');\n	$(''#content_msg'').val('''');\n$(''.pa1'').hide();\n}\n</script>\n', '1104071759050696798', 1311780740, 1317290240, '1105260920487534578', 8, ''),
