('sxf_article_home_category_fengcai', '?template("sxf_article_head")?\r\n<div class="fengcai_menu">\r\n    <div class="connect">\r\n    <a>前言</a>\r\n    <a href="?site(''article/home/category/335396'')?">历任领导</a>\r\n    <a href="?site(''article/home/category/335442'')?">关怀激励</a>\r\n    <a href="?site(''article/home/category/335551'')?">风雨历程</a>\r\n    <a href="?site(''article/home/category/335690'')?">卫士风采</a>\r\n    <a href="?site(''article/home/category/335721'')?">荣誉谱</a>\r\n    <a href="?site(''article/home/category/335828'')?">宋文博</a>\r\n    <a>后记</a>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fengcai_top">\r\n    <div class="ct">邵阳消防官兵为了人民的安居乐业，时刻坚守岗位，默奉献青春。灭火救援战斗中，他们勇往直前，关键时刻把生的希望留给别人，把死的威胁留给自己，用自己的实际行动诠释一个消防兵的生命价值，用青春年华抒写人生的辉煌；监督执法中，他们恪尽职守、常抓不懈，务实细致的工作，彻底根除了火患的威胁，大增强了人民群众的消防安全意识，为人民群众开辟了一条生命的康庄大道，撑起了一把财产安全的庇护伞。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fengcai_center">\r\n    <div class="fengcai_zc">\r\n      <div class="mg">\r\n         <object classid="clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=7,0,19,0" width="780" height="250">\r\n         <param name="movie" value="imageshow.swf" />\r\n         <param name="quality" value="high" />\r\n         <param name="wmode" value="transparent" />\r\n         <embed src="?site(''res/sxf/imageshow.swf'')?" width="780" height="250" quality="high" pluginspage="http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" wmode="transparent"></embed>\r\n        </object>\r\n     </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class="fengcai_pa"><img src="?res(''res/sxf/img/zc.jpg'')?" /></div>\r\n     <div class="fengcai_zq"><img src="?res(''res/sxf/img/zc.jpg'')?" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n?template("sxf_article_foot")?\r\n', '1204251659419211169', 1335966460, 1336208260, '1204251659419211169', 8, ''),
