m" target="_blank">Test 1</a>/<a href="http://www.javaeye.com" target="_blank">Test 2</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://lt-login.heshengfang.com.cn:880" target="_blank">Preview</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://lt.hsfvip.com" target="_blank">Release</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n</div>\n<div class="actions">\n<ul>\n<li>命名规范</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n <div style="padding-left: 35px">\n1.函数命名，所有控制器函数名小写，Model，VO等其它函数名字首大写<br />\n2.model对象字首小写，带model后缀，例如CategoryModel categoryModel = new CategoryModel();<br />\n3.vo对象字首小写，带VO后缀，例如CategoryVO categoryVO = categoryModel.Get(category_id);<br />\n4.表单命名必须跟表字段命名一致\n<br />\n</div>\n<div class="actions">\n<ul>\n<li>SVN地址</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n <div style="padding-left: 35px">\nhttp://svn.b2cup.com:880/svn/Poject/<br />\n</div>\n?template("base_foot")?  ', '1105260920487534578', 1309193860, 1313682560, '1107011422383972432', 5, '');
